achine-Lungs-full-London-show-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/FlorenceAndTheMachine-Lungs-full-London-show-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/FlorenceAndTheMachine-Lungs-full-London-show-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/FlorenceAndTheMachine-Lungs-full-London-show-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/FlorenceAndTheMachine-Lungs-full-London-show-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/florence-and-the-machine">Florence + The Machine</a>将在伦敦举办的一场特别管弦乐演出中完整演奏他们的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-florence-and-the-machine-10635-316456#:~:text=a%20shower%20in%20the%20Australian%20jungle.&amp;text=that%20'Lungs'%20is%20so%20distinctly%E2%80%A6%20OK.&amp;text=only%20because%20it%20could%20have,Stripes%20that%20it's%20almost%20laughable.">《Lungs》</a> ——详情请见下文。</p><p>该乐队将于 9 月 11 日星期三在历史悠久的皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅首次亮相<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/articles/2kSNxH9Cj9PT62ZzTnvWpYZ/the-bbc-proms-whats-it-all-about" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BBC 逍遥音乐节</a>，这也是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/florence-welch">弗洛伦斯·韦尔奇 (Florence Welch)</a>及其合作伙伴今年在英国的唯一演出。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/florence-and-the-machine-manchester-ao-arena-live-review-setlist-photos-3392487">《Florence + The Machine》在曼彻斯特现场直播：舞蹈热潮的宣泄和欣快爆发</a></strong></li></ul><p>韦尔奇在 <a href="https://www.vogue.co.uk/article/florence-welch-proms" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国版《Vogue》</em></a>的最新采访中宣布了这场音乐会的消息。 “当[邀请]到来时，他们的反应是，‘我们知道你要离开，但你愿意……吗？’我当时就想，‘是的！’，”她告诉该刊物。</p><p>该媒体指出，这位主唱“目前正在为即将到来的演出寻找古老的中世纪英国乐器”，这场演出被称为“佛罗伦萨+机器——肺交响曲”。</p><p> “我很荣幸，”韦尔奇继续说道。 “我家里的生活背景是古典音乐，尤其是那些比较晦涩的东西。因此，被邀请参加音乐节真是一件令人兴奋的事情——逍遥音乐节是如此特别。”</p><p>荣获<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">全英音乐奖</a>的《Lungs》于 2009 年发行，收录了单曲《Dog Days Are Over》、《Rabbit Heart (Raise It Up)》、《Cosmic Love》和《You&#39;ve Got The Love》。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C6LRZrxiaPo/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.1